*********-HANDLING ALERTS IN SELENIUM-*****************

WHAT IS ALERT?
 Alert is the popup message that u get on your application.
 Alert takes the focus og our main screen/page.
 We can not proceed until we have handle this alert.


TYPES OF ALERTS :
 1.webBase Alerts/html Alerts : We can simply inspect them and deal with them in a regular way
 2.javaScript Alert : We can handle these alerts by using Alert interface in Selenium.
 3.Window base Alert : we can't handle them in Selenium.



 Authentication alert:
 information inside the url

 admin:admin
 password

 URL: https://admin:admin@the-internet.herokuapp.com/basic_auth
